						<p class="pt-intro">Welcome to the Personal Training Section With our great local and regional reputation for consistent results and hard work toward our clients you can be sure whichever way you choose to train, you're in the best hands.</p>
						<div class="pt-info">
							<div class="text">
								<p>Personal Training is the closest we can get to physically moving in with you and stopping you from straying from your diet and not training! We literally monitor everything down to a tee and focus on the individual and what he/she wants both physically and mentally out of the experience.</p>

								<p>We include, weekly sessions based on affordability (Price list below), Full bespoke nutrition and home/gym workout programmes and most importantly 24 hour support. We see almost every meal you eat via WhatsApp and ensure you're on the right track with your training.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="text">

								<p><strong>Grab your FREE Personal Training consultation now and we will answer all of your questions and suggest an affordable package based on your goals and result expectations!</strong></p>

